Hello Engr. Smith,

We are excited to have you as one of the Teaching Assistants in [Technical Interview Prep Course][1]. The goal of this 12-week virtual course is to help the students ace technical interviews by preparing them to solve challenging algorithm problems in real whiteboard interviews at top companies. We have three levels for this course: [Beginner][2], [Intermediate][3], and [Advanced][4]. 

To help us know more about you, please fill-out this [form][5]. It will also aid us to learn about your topic preference, availability, and other necessary information.

For any questions, feel free to reach us through <a href="mailto:volunteers@codepath.org">volunteers@codepath.org</a>. In case you would want to get involved in other ways, please check [Codepath Volunteer Page][6] and let us know. We are thrilled to have you be part of our cause. 

Looking forward to working with you!

Sincerely,
CodePath.org Team



